<h6><b>Important Security Information:</b></h6>
<p>
	The Application is collecting background GPS location in the app is to alert the user about movement so that the user can update the server about the purpose, which in this case is only to communicate Clock-In and Clock- Out time. People move in and out of various facilities, however need to update the server ONLY for the Clock-In and Clock-Out time, so that the Time and Attendance table is updated, for records. This data is highly secure and a private, which data is pushed to the server only, for intended users only. The data is not used for any other purpose.
</p>
 

